OL,3,CEx-pupil says children 'wrongfully
OL,4,Crestrained' at closed Cumbria school
OL,6,FBailey Roberts said physical restraint
OL,7,Fwasn't used as a last resort by some
OL,8,Fstaff at Wings School
OL,10,FA former pupil of a residential school
OL,11,Fin Cumbria has spoken out about the
OL,12,Fyears of "trauma" experienced as a
OL,13,Fresult of his time there.
OL,15,FBailey Roberts said he "witnessed
OL,16,Fpupils being slammed up against the
OL,17,Fwall", while a pupil at Wings between
OL,18,F2011 and 2015.
