OL,3,CEx-pupil says children 'wrongfully
OL,4,Crestrained' at closed Cumbria school
OL,6,F"There's been times when I've heard
OL,7,Fpupils reporting that they've had body
OL,8,Fparts hit on tables, and they've been
OL,9,Fwrongfully restrained, when it
OL,10,Fshouldn't have been the case," he said.
OL,12,FWings School Cumbria, which was near
OL,13,FKendal, opened in 2003 and looked
OL,14,Fafter pupils with social, emotional
OL,15,Fand mental health difficulties. In
OL,16,FJuly 2024, it closed following a
OL,17,Fsurprise Ofsted inspection which found
OL,18,Fpupils had been subject to "excessive
OL,19,Fforce".
