OL,3,CEx-pupil says children 'wrongfully
OL,4,Crestrained' at closed Cumbria school
OL,6,F"Some leaders and staff use
OL,7,Frestrictive physical intervention on
OL,8,Fpupils as a strategy for discipline
OL,9,Fand compliance, not solely when pupils
OL,10,For staff are at risk of harm,"
OL,11,FOfsted's inspectors wrote at the time.
OL,13,F"The school's physical intervention
OL,14,Fpractice is unsafe with pupils subject
OL,15,Fto excessive force and unsafe holds."
