OL,3,CEx-pupil says children 'wrongfully
OL,4,Crestrained' at closed Cumbria school
OL,6,FIn December, ITV News Border reported
OL,7,Fthat claims of abuse are now being
OL,8,Finvestigated by Cumbria Police under
OL,9,FOperation Falcon, and multiple former
OL,10,Fpupils are considering taking civil
OL,11,Faction against the school's owners.
OL,13,FAccording to guidelines published by
OL,14,Fthe UK Government, physical force
OL,15,Fshould only be used by school staff
OL,16,Fagainst children as a last resort,
OL,17,Fwhen a pupil is at risk of harming
OL,18,Fthemselves, or others.
