OL,6,F"It was in their guidelines to be used
OL,7,Fas a last resort - it wasn't," said Mr
OL,8,FRoberts.
OL,10,FHe added that a "handful of the staff"
OL,11,Fused physical force as a "go-to".
OL,13,F"Kind of an abuse of power over a
OL,14,Fpupil," he said.
OL,16,FHis time at Wings School has led to
OL,17,F"trauma", he said, adding that "a lot
OL,18,Fof my characteristics, a lot of my
OL,19,Fmannerisms, how I go about my day to
OL,20,Fday life has been impacted by Wings".
