OL,6,FMultiple local authorities across the
OL,7,Fnorth of England sent pupils to Wings
OL,8,Fwhile it was in operation.
OL,10,FOne of those was Cumbria County
OL,11,FCouncil, which ITV News Border can
OL,12,Freveal spent almost #10m in five years
OL,13,Fplacing pupils at the independent
OL,14,Fresidential school.
