OL,6,FAsked what checks were taken to ensure
OL,7,Fpupils were safe, the successors to
OL,8,FCumbria County Council responded.
OL,9,FCumberland Council said: "We are one
OL,10,Fof 11 Local Authorities who had placed
OL,11,Fchildren at Wings School. Their care
OL,12,Fand safety is our paramount priority.
OL,13,FWe took immediate action and removed
OL,14,Fthem from the school as soon as issues
OL,15,Fwere raised by Ofsted."
