OL,6,FAnd Westmorland and Furness Council
OL,7,Fadded: "Alongside several other local
OL,8,Fauthorities in the North of England,
OL,9,Fwe were instructed by Ofsted to find
OL,10,Falternative provision for children
OL,11,Fplaced at Wings school earlier this
OL,12,Fyear, which we did."
OL,14,FMiddlesborough Council, which was
OL,15,Fresponsible for Mr Roberts, said it
OL,16,Fwouldn't be appropriate to comment on
OL,17,Fhis situation given the ongoing police
OL,18,Finvestigation.
