OL,6,FWings was rated as 'good' by school
OL,7,Fstandards authority Ofsted in 2012,
OL,8,F2014, 2017, and 2021.
OL,10,FBut Mr Roberts claims some school
OL,11,Fstaff attempted to interfere with
OL,12,Finspections whilst he was a pupil at
OL,13,FWings.
OL,15,F"When Ofsted came round to do their
OL,16,Freports, often it was very hush-hush,"
OL,17,Fhe said.
