OL,4,Crestrained' at closed Cumbria school
OL,6,F"Staff would tell you what to do,
OL,7,Fwhere to be. And if you were labelled
OL,8,Fas one of the 'bad ones' they kind of
OL,9,Fkept you away, and kept the good ones
OL,10,Fin sight of Ofsted to give them a
OL,11,Fbetter impression. It would happen
OL,12,Fevery time Ofsted would show up."
OL,14,FOfsted didn't respond to these
OL,15,Fspecific allegations. In a statement,
OL,16,Fa spokesperson said: "It is very
OL,17,Fupsetting to hear allegations of abuse
OL,18,Ffrom pupils at Wings School.
OL,19,FSafeguarding is central to our
OL,20,Finspections and we take it extremely
OL,21,Fseriously."
