OL,7,FGroup, which ran Wings and has schools
OL,8,Faround the UK, said, "we are fully
OL,9,Fcooperating with the on-going external
OL,10,Finvestigation and we will continue to
OL,11,Fassist however we can.
OL,13,F"At this time, and to our knowledge,
OL,14,Fno claim of misconduct relating to any
